reviews.review_text: Train! This was an incredible show. I remember how excited everyone was when they heard that train~
Awesome! This show was incredible.  My mother passed away the same night so it has special meaning too.  Highly recommended.

My first show!!! It was an amazing night! Not JUST because it was my first. Great show through and through. And when Mickey, I think, came out with the shoulder straps of horns to announce (I'm all messed up) Casey Jones!!!!...priceless!!! What an end to one memorable evening!!!
